             Position finish,

        Create a new instance of a level with the specified parameters.
        Parameters:
        start - player spawn point.
        finish - level finish position.
        levelNumber - level number. Levels are player in order of level number.
        levelName - name of the level.
        width - width in cells of the level.
        height - height in cells of the level.
